msgid "Wagtail redirects"
msgstr "Wagtail troka dalan"

msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipu"

msgid "Permanent"
msgstr "Permanente"

msgid "Temporary"
msgstr "Temporaria"

msgid "All"
msgstr "Hotu"

msgid "From site"
msgstr "Husi sítiu"

msgid "All sites"
msgstr "situs sira hotu"

msgid "A redirect with this path already exists."
msgstr "Troko dalan ho parte ne'ebe mak existi tiha ona"

msgid "File to import"
msgstr "Arkivu atu importa"

#, python-format
msgid "Supported formats: %(supported_formats)s."
msgstr "Suporta formatu: %(supported_formats)s."

msgid "From field"
msgstr "Hosi kampu"

msgid "To field"
msgstr "Ba kampu"

msgid "redirect from"
msgstr "Troka dalan husi"

msgid "site"
msgstr "sítiu"

msgid "permanent"
msgstr "permanente"

msgid ""
"Recommended. Permanent redirects ensure search engines forget the old page "
"(the 'Redirect from') and index the new page instead."
msgstr ""
"Rekomenda ona. Rediresaun permanente sira asegura katak motor buka sira "
"haluha pajina tuan ('Rediresaun hosi') no indeksa fali pajina foun deit."

msgid "redirect to a page"
msgstr "rediresaun ba pajina ida"

msgid "target page route"
msgstr "alvu rota pajina"

msgid ""
"Optionally specify a route on the target page to redirect to. Leave blank to "
"redirect to the default page route."
msgstr ""
"Opsionalmente espesifika rota ida iha pajina alvu atu rediresiona ba. Husik "
"mamuk hodi rediresiona ba rota pajina padraun."

msgid "redirect to any URL"
msgstr "rediresaun ba URL ruma"

msgid "automatically created"
msgstr "Kria ona ho automátika"

msgid "created at"
msgstr "Kria iha"

msgid "temporary"
msgstr "Temporariu"

msgid "redirect"
msgstr "rediresaun"

msgid "redirects"
msgstr "rediresaun sira"

msgid "Redirects"
msgstr "Rediresaun sira"

msgid "Import redirects"
msgstr "Importa rediresaun sira"

msgid ""
"<p>Select a file where redirects are separated into rows and contains the "
"columns representing <code>from</code> and <code>to</code> (they can be "
"named anything).</p> <p>After submitting you will be taken to a confirmation "
"view where you can customize your redirects before import.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Hili arkivu ida iha ne'ebé rediresaun sira haketak ba liña sira no "
"kontein koluna sira ne'ebé reprezenta <code> husi </code> no <code> ba </"
"code> (sira bele hanaran saida de'it). </p> <p>Hafoin submete ita-boot sei "
"lori ba iha konfirmasaun ida iha ne'ebé ita-boot bele personaliza ita-boot "
"nia rediresaun sira molok importa.</p>"

msgid "Import"
msgstr "Importa"

#, python-format
msgid "Delete redirect %(title)s"
msgstr "hamoos rediresaun %(title)s"

msgid "Are you sure you want to delete this redirect?"
msgstr "Ita serteza hakarak hamoos rediresaun ida-ne'e?"

msgid "Confirm import"
msgstr "Konfirma importa"

msgid "Confirm"
msgstr "Konfirma"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Kansela"

msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Pré-visualizasaun"

msgid "Summary"
msgstr "Sumáriu"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Found %(total)s redirects, created %(successes)s and found %(errors)s errors."
msgstr ""
"Hetan ona rediresaun %(total)s, kria ona %(successes)s no hetan ona erru "
"%(errors)s"

msgid "From"
msgstr "Husi"

msgid "To"
msgstr "Ba "

msgid "Error"
msgstr "Erru"

msgid "Continue"
msgstr "Kontinua"

#, python-format
msgid "Sorry, no redirects match \"<em>%(query_string)s</em>\""
msgstr "Deskulpa, laiha rediresaun koresponde \"<em>%(query_string)s</em>\""

#, python-format
msgid ""
"No redirects have been created. Why not <a "
"href=\"%(wagtailredirects_add_redirect_url)s\">add one</a>?"
msgstr ""
"Laiha rediresaun sira ne'ebé kria ona. Tamba sa la <a "
"href=\"%(wagtailredirects_add_redirect_url)s\">aumenta ida</a>?"

msgid "Add redirect"
msgstr "Aumenta rediresaun"

msgid "Site"
msgstr "sítiu"

msgid "The redirect could not be saved due to errors."
msgstr "Rediresaun labele salva tamba erru sira."

#, python-format
msgid "Redirect '%(redirect_title)s' updated."
msgstr "Rediresaun '%(redirect_title)s' atualiza ona"

#, python-format
msgid "Redirect '%(redirect_title)s' deleted."
msgstr "Rediresaun '%(redirect_title)s' hamoos ona."

msgid "The redirect could not be created due to errors."
msgstr "Rediresaun labele salva tamba erru sira."

#, python-format
msgid "Redirect '%(redirect_title)s' added."
msgstr "Rediresaun '%(redirect_title)s' aumenta ona."

msgid "Search redirects"
msgstr "Buka rediresaun sira"

#, python-format
msgid "File format of type \"%(extension)s\" is not supported."
msgstr "Tipu arkivu nia formatu \"%(extension)s\" la suporta."

#, python-format
msgid "Imported file has a wrong encoding: %(error_message)s."
msgstr "Arkivu ne'ebé importa iha kodifikasaun ne'ebé sala: %(error_message)s."

#, python-format
msgid "%(error)s encountered while trying to read file: %(filename)s."
msgstr "Hasoru ona %(error)s bainhira koko atu lee arkivu: %(filename)s"

#, python-format
msgid "Imported %(total)d redirect"
msgid_plural "Imported %(total)d redirects"
msgstr[0] "Importa ona rediresaun %(total)d"
